strings: <voice_0x01000C0A><se_def>China: Where there's a sign, it's easy
<voice_0x01000C0C><se_def>China: Evil strikes again... No, it's not a crime... Even worse...
<voice_0x01000C0D><se_def>China: It was so bad... like the demons of hell were playing together...
<voice_0x01000C10><se_def>China: It stands for<:> Marcel! you you you you it's magic. What happened and who's there?
<voice_0x01000C11><se_def>China: That's the worst! You must not move
<voice_0x01000C12><se_def>China: This is...! Did you take me here?
<voice_0x01000C13><se_def>China: Not important! I need your help! last time, huh? ...
<voice_0x01000C14><se_def>China: It needs to be done quickly. maybe we ate too much
<voice_0x01000C15><se_def>China: The door was locked from the inside. You have to destroy it! do everything!
